[image]


[ingredients]
1/2 tsp coconut oil
2 cloves garlic
25g onion
40g pepper
30g carrot
40g red wine
1 tsp cumin
1/2 tsp oregano
1/4 tsp paprika
1/4 tsp cayenne paprika
130g passata
260g cooked beans
50g corn
75g rice
200ml water
[ingredients]

[steps]
Cook the rice and saute the vegetables.
Add the red wine and cook on high heat until alcohol evaporates.
Add everything else and cook for 30-40 minutes
[steps]

